column2: SELECT top # gS.specObjID as ID, gS.sfr_tot_p5# as gS_Total, gS.sfr_fib_p5# as gS_Fibre, gS.specsfr_tot_p5# as gS_TotalSpec, gS.specsfr_fib_p5# as gS_FibreSpec, SFP.SFR as SFP, PP.SFR as PP, GED.ssfr as GED, GED.ssfr_mean as GED_Mean, GEND.ssfr as GEND, GEND.ssfr_mean as GEND_Mean, WD.ssfr as WD, WD.ssfr_mean as WD_Mean, WND.ssfr as WND, WND.ssfr_mean as WND_Mean FROM galSpecExtra gS JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyDust GED on gS.specObjID = GED.specObjID JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyNoDust GEND on gS.specObjID = GEND.specObjID JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust GWD on gS.specObjID = GWD.specObjID JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideNoDust GWND on gS.specObjID = GWND.specObjID JOIN stellarMassStarformingPort SFP on gS.specObjID = SFP.specObjID JOIN stellarMassPassivePort PP on gS.specObjID = PP.specObjID WHERE gS.specObjID ! = # AND gS.sfr_tot_p5# ! = # AND gS.sfr_fib_p5# ! = # AND gS.specsfr_tot_p5# ! = # AND gS.specsfr_fib_p5# ! = # AND SFP.SFR ! = # AND PP.SFR ! = # AND GED.ssfr ! = # AND GED.ssfr_mean ! = # AND GEND.ssfr ! = # AND GEND.ssfr_mean ! = # AND WD.ssfr ! = # AND WD.ssfr_mean ! = # AND WND.ssfr ! = # AND WND.ssfr_mean ! = #
